message.content:
Redesign the sidebar in `/Users/admin/it-asset/components/layout/sidebar.tsx` for a professional enterprise asset management system. Style: "fusion" — Linear/Notion modern aesthetic + enterprise functionality.

Read the file first, then make changes.

## Changes

### 1. Organize nav items into groups

Add a `group?: string` field to `NavItem`. Group the items:

```typescript
export type NavItem = {
  label: string;
  href: string;
  icon: LucideIcon;
  roles: UserRole[];
  group?: string;
};

const navItems: NavItem[] = [
  // 工作台
  { label: "首页", href: "/home", icon: LayoutDashboard, roles: ["EMPLOYEE", "MANAGER", "IT_ADMIN", "EXECUTIVE"], group: "工作台" },
  // 资产与工单
  { label: "我的资产", href: "/my-assets", icon: Laptop, roles: ["EMPLOYEE", "MANAGER"], group: "资产与工单" },
  { label: "申领设备", href: "/apply", icon: ClipboardPlus, roles: ["EMPLOYEE", "MANAGER"], group: "资产与工单" },
  { label: "我的工单", href: "/tickets", icon: Ticket, roles: ["EMPLOYEE", "MANAGER"], group: "资产与工单" },
  // 工具
  { label: "AI 助手", href: "/chat", icon: Bot, roles: ["EMPLOYEE", "MANAGER", "IT_ADMIN", "EXECUTIVE"], group: "工具" },
  { label: "通知中心", href: "/notifications", icon: Bell, roles: ["EMPLOYEE", "MANAGER", "IT_ADMIN", "EXECUTIVE"], group: "工具" },
  { label: "个人设置", href: "/profile", icon: Settings, roles: ["EMPLOYEE", "MANAGER", "IT_ADMIN", "EXECUTIVE"], group: "工具" },
  // 管理
  { label: "审批工作台", href: "/approvals", icon: CheckSquare, roles: ["MANAGER"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "部门看板", href: "/dept-board", icon: BarChart3, roles: ["MANAGER"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "IT 工作台", href: "/it/home", icon: Wrench, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "工单工作台", href: "/it/tickets", icon: Ticket, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "资产管理", href: "/it/assets", icon: Package, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "型号管理", href: "/it/models", icon: Archive, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "入库操作", href: "/it/inbound", icon: Boxes, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "盘点", href: "/it/inventory", icon: ClipboardList, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "用户管理", href: "/it/users", icon: Users, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  { label: "审计日志", href: "/it/audit", icon: FileText, roles: ["IT_ADMIN"], group: "管理" },
  // 数据
  { label: "资产大屏", href: "/exec/dashboard", icon: PieChart, roles: ["EXECUTIVE"], group: "数据" },
  { label: "AI 洞察", href: "/exec/insights", icon: Lightbulb, roles: ["EXECUTIVE"], group: "数据" },
];
```

### 2. Update the render logic

Group items by `group` field. Within the `<nav>` element:

```tsx
{/* Group items by group label */}
{Object.entries(
  filteredItems.reduce((acc, item) => {
    const g = item.group ?? "";
    if (!acc[g]) acc[g] = [];
    acc[g].push(item);
    return acc;
  }, {} as Record<string, NavItem[]>)
).map(([group, items]) => (
  <div key={group} className="mb-2">
    {!collapsed && group && (
      <div className="px-2 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sidebar-foreground/35">
        {group}
      </div>
    )}
    {items.map((item) => {
      // ... existing nav item rendering
    })}
  </div>
))}
```

### 3. Active state with left border accent

Instead of just `bg-sidebar-accent`, add a left border for the active item:

```tsx
className={cn(
  "flex items-center gap-3 rounded-md px-2 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-150 border-l-2",
  "hover:bg-sidebar-accent hover:text-sidebar-accent-foreground",
  isActive
    ? "bg-sidebar-accent text-sidebar-accent-foreground border-l-primary"
    : "text-sidebar-foreground/70 border-l-transparent",
  collapsed && "justify-center px-0 py-2 border-l-0",
)}
```

### 4. Brand area polish

Make the brand area more refined:
- The logo container: add a subtle gradient or use `bg-primary/10` background
- The system name: use `font-bold` instead of `font-semibold`
- Remove the department/name subtitle (clutters the brand area), keep just the system name

New brand area:
```tsx
{collapsed ? (
  <div className="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold ring-1 ring-primary/20">
    IT
  </div>
) : (
  <div className="flex items-center gap-2.5 overflow-hidden">
    <div className="flex size-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold ring-1 ring-primary/20">
      IT
    </div>
    <div className="min-w-0">
      <div className="truncate text-sm font-bold tracking-tight">IT资产管理系统</div>
    </div>
  </div>
)}
```

### 5. Role debug panel — minimize

Remove the `<Separator />` (it's always visible). Move the role debug panel to be less prominent:

```tsx
{/* Role debug - collapsed to bottom, tiny */}
<div className="mt-auto border-t border-sidebar-border p-1.5">
  <div className={cn("flex", collapsed ? "flex-col gap-0.5" : "flex-wrap gap-0.5")}>
    {allRoles.map((role) => {
      const roleLabels: Record<UserRole, string> = {
        EMPLOYEE: "员工", MANAGER: "经理", IT_ADMIN: "IT", EXECUTIVE: "高管",
      };
      const isActive = user.role === role;
      return (
        <button
          key={role}
          onClick={() => setRole(role)}
          title={collapsed ? roleLabels[role] : undefined}
          className={cn(
            "rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-medium transition-colors",
            isActive
              ? "bg-sidebar-primary text-sidebar-primary-foreground"
              : "text-sidebar-foreground/40 hover:text-sidebar-foreground/70",
            collapsed && "px-0 py-1 text-center text-[9px]",
          )}
        >
          {collapsed ? roleLabels[role].slice(0, 1) : roleLabels[role]}
        </button>
      );
    })}
  </div>
</div>
```

Note: wrap the entire sidebar content between brand and collapse-toggle in a flex column. The role debug panel should be separate, just above the collapse toggle. Remove the existing `<Separator />` before the role debug section.

The structural layout should be:
1. Brand area (top)
2. Navigation with scroll (flex-1)
3. Role debug panel (bottom, above collapse toggle)
4. Collapse toggle (bottom, last element)

## VERIFICATION
After editing, run `npx tsc --noEmit` from `/Users/admin/it-asset/` and fix any errors.

